The Glenn Beck Program

      The Glenn Beck Program - 11/11/13Monday, November 11, 2013 11:01 AM





It's Veteran's Day and Glenn salutes all American veterans.

  Also, Obama distancing his name from the debacle of Obamacare,
    by no longer calling it Obamacare,

      and even the Left realizes the president is done.

  Plus, 7 steps for the unemployed and why work is so important,
